      <div class="sec-eyebrow"><span class="num">02</span> Featured work</div>
      <h2 class="sec-title">Dream DeCypher — <em>play on web-browser (PC or Mobile).</em></h2>
      <p class="sec-sub">A 100% context-based language learning puzzle game set inside a detective game. I led a team of three from concept to a shipped, playable build — presented at Supercell Games First 2026.</p>
