          <p class="proj-desc">Dream DeCypher is a language detective puzzle game. Listen. Observe. Decode. Connect. Crack the case. Currently available in Mandarin Chinese for decoding. <b>No prior language knowledge needed</b> — just jump in, solve puzzles, and the language will unlock itself.</p>
