        <div class="contrib"><h4>I designed</h4><p>Core puzzle loop and game logic progression — players "solve" a language through context, logic and gameplay. The closest experience to how a baby learns its first language.</p></div>
        <div class="contrib"><h4>I drove</h4><p>User-acquisition strategy, metric analysis, and the funding pitch that secured a Startup Foundation Grant.</p></div>
